name: Captain Morena (F-Zero Fan Game)
description: Captain Morena, an Asian-Cyborg woman racer, must find extra spare parts to upgrade  her racing vehicle, the Valiant Horse number 999 before the race challenge versus Captain Swallow, a wild and menacing  racer. This is a fan-made F-Zero game on Bitsy.  All rights to F-Zero developers. If you want to play the game with music (if you wish), download my html GitHub file. Enjoy!!!!
